node.text:
On this day 27 years ago (May 1, 1994), Ayrton Senna lost his life after his car left the racing line at Tamburello, Imola 🇮🇹, ran in a straight line off the track and struck an unprotected concrete barrier.
On the video you can see one of his masterful laps in Monaco at the 1990 GP 🇲🇨
Rest in peace to the greatest #SempreSenna A legend lives on!

node.text:
Scariest sounding airplane ever? 
The Vulcan XH558 is a jet-powered tailless delta wing high-altitude strategic bomber, which was operated by the RAF from 1956 until 1984. A popular feature of XH558 at flypasts and air shows is the so-called “Vulcan Howl”, a distinctive sound made by some Vulcan airframes when the engines are at approximately 90 percent power, due to the arrangement of the air intakes. #bigtoys
